		</div>
	</div>


</div>


				<div style="width: 90%;" class="figure-inner">
						<a class="lightbox" href="/img/figure/figure1_2.jpg" data-title='Figure 1.2 Historical Trends in Unit Costs and Deployment of Low-Carbon Energy Technologies in the United States'>
							<picture>
		<source media="(min-width: 1200px)" srcset="/img/styles/figure1_2-1200.jpg, /img/styles/figure1_2-1200@2x.jpg 2x">
		<source media="(min-width: 992px)" srcset="/img/styles/figure1_2-992.jpg, /img/styles/figure1_2-992@2x.jpg 2x">
