	    <th label="Region: " scope="row">Southwest</th>
	    <td label="Action: ">In response to severe drought, seven Colorado River basin states, the US and Mexican governments, and Indigenous Peoples are collaborating to improve water conservation and develop adaptation solutions. Dozens of cities are committed to emissions reductions; for instance, Phoenix is on track to meet a 2030 goal of 50% reduction in greenhouse gas emissions from 2018 levels. {Ch. <a target="_blank" href="/chapter/28#section-1">28, Introduction</a>; Box <a target="_blank" href="/chapter/28#box-28_1">28.1</a>}</td>
	</tr>
