	</tr>
	<tr class="odd">
	    <th scope="row">Alaska</th>
	    <td>
	        <div class="td-icon">
	    	    <span>Landscape degradation increases damage to private and municipal infrastructure. <br>{<a target="_blank" href="/chapter/29#key-message-2">29.2</a>, <a target="_blank" href="/chapter/29#key-message-4">29.4</a>}</span>
	    	    <img alt="Infrastructure icon" src="/img/1/Table1_2_icons-01.svg" style="width:30px; height:30px; padding-right: 5px;"/>
		    </div>
	    </td>
	    <td>
	        <div class="td-icon">
	        	<span>Reduced fish stocks harm local economies, Tribal sovereignty, and overall well-being. <br>{<a target="_blank" href="/chapter/29#key-message-6">29.6</a>, <a target="_blank" href="/chapter/29#key-message-7">29.7</a>}</span>
	        	<img alt="Economy icon" src="/img/1/Table1_2_icons-07.svg" style="width:30px; height:30px; padding-right: 5px;"/>
