	    	    <img alt="Food security icon" src="/img/1/Table1_2_icons-05.svg" style="width:30px; height:30px; padding-right: 5px;"/>
		    </div>
	    </td>
	    <td>
	        <div class="td-icon">
	    	    <span>Diminished access to mammals, seabirds, fish, and vegetation decreases local food security. <br>{<a target="_blank" href="/chapter/29#key-message-5">29.5</a>}</span>
	    	    <img alt="Food security icon" src="/img/1/Table1_2_icons-05.svg" style="width:30px; height:30px; padding-right: 5px;"/>
